 <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">Casimir effect for Chern–Simons layers in the vacuum</subfield>
  <subfield code="9">Springer</subfield>
 </datafield>
 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We solve the diffraction problem for electromagnetic waves on a planar (2+1)-dimensional layer with a given Chern–Simons action. The Casimir energy of a system of two parallel planar Chern–Simons layers is expressed in terms of the coefficients of reflection from separate layers.</subfield>
